recommendation.new_prompt_text:
Decompose this problem into exactly two mathematical subproblems to comply with system constraints. 

Helper 1 must perform a formal scaling or dimensional analysis to derive the general theoretical formula for the requested parameter. 
Helper 2 must rigorously test the formula derived by Helper 1 against the specific list of mathematical instances provided in the question to ensure the formula is universally consistent across all cases.

Constraint: You must request exactly two helpers. Do not request more than two. 

Each helper must receive a single, focused mathematical task using plain text only. Do not use markdown, code fences, or LaTeX-style backslashes in helper instructions.

Return exactly one JSON object in this format:
{
  "schema_name": "eywa_node_response",
  "schema_version": "v1",
  "orchestration_decision": "delegate",
  "decision_notes": "optional string",
  "helpers": [
    {
      "label": "helper_1",
      "instructions": "plain-text subproblem for the first helper"
    },
    {
      "label": "helper_2",
      "instructions": "plain-text subproblem for the second helper"
    }
  ],
  "synthesis_brief": "how the parent should combine the child results"
}

